# Frontend testing conventions

- Prefer Testing Library `*ByRole` queries first (`*ByLabelText` when appropriate).
- Use `userEvent.setup()` and `await` user interactions.
- Test loading and error states for async/data-driven UI.
- Keep tests colocated with implementation files.
- For reducers/thunks, use project helpers (`reducerTester`, `thunkTester`) where applicable.
- For one-shot local runs, prefer non-watch commands (for example `yarn jest --no-watch`).

